<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Nueva solicitud de pedido — Citribio</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f5f3ee;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1a2e1c;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f5f3ee;">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding:36px 12px;">

      <!-- ── Email card ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
             style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);">

        <!-- ── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="background-color:#567f0b;padding:32px 36px 28px;">
            {% if logoGrandeUrl %}
              <img src="{{ logoGrandeUrl }}" alt="Citribio"
                   style="display:block;margin:0 auto 20px;height:60px;width:auto;max-width:220px;" />
            {% else %}
              <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin-bottom:14px;">CITRIBIO</div>
            {% endif %}
            <h1 style="margin:0 0 10px;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.25;">
              Nueva solicitud de pedido
            </h1>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.88);line-height:1.6;">
              Has recibido una nueva solicitud de pedido. Revisa los productos, confirma disponibilidad y envía el presupuesto final al cliente.
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Action notice ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 36px 0;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="background-color:#fff8f0;border-left:4px solid #ff731d;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:16px 20px;">
                  <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#cc5a10;margin-bottom:6px;">⚠ Acción requerida</div>
                  <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#7a3a0a;line-height:1.65;">
                    Este pedido debe ser revisado por el distribuidor antes de confirmar el precio final, el envío y la preparación.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Order + Customer data ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:24px 36px 0;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>

                <!-- Order data -->
                <td width="44%" valign="top" style="padding-right:10px;">
                  <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#7a7060;margin-bottom:10px;">Datos del pedido</div>
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                         style="background-color:#f8f6f2;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Nº Pedido</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">#{{ order.id }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Fecha</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">{{ order.createdAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Estado</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">
                        <span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#fff8f0;color:#cc5a10;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid #ffd0a8;">
                          En revisión
                        </span>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;white-space:nowrap;">Nº productos</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;">{{ items|length }}</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>

                <!-- Customer data -->
                <td width="56%" valign="top" style="padding-left:10px;">
                  <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#7a7060;margin-bottom:10px;">Datos del cliente</div>
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                         style="background-color:#f8f6f2;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Nombre</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">{{ (user.name ~ ' ' ~ user.lastName)|trim ?: 'N/D' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Email</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;word-break:break-all;">
                        <a href="mailto:{{ user.email|e }}" style="color:#567f0b;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">{{ user.email ?: 'N/D' }}</a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">Teléfono</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">
                        {% if user.phone %}
                          <a href="tel:{{ user.phone|e }}" style="color:#567f0b;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">{{ user.phone }}</a>
                        {% else %}
                          <span style="color:#a09880;">N/D</span>
                        {% endif %}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    {% if user.dni %}
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;white-space:nowrap;">DNI</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #e6e0d4;">{{ user.dni }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endif %}
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;white-space:nowrap;vertical-align:top;">Dirección</td>
                      <td style="padding:11px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#1a2e1c;line-height:1.5;">{{ order.deliveryAddressSnapshot ?: 'N/D' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>

              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Products table ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:28px 36px 0;">
            <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:#1a2e1c;margin-bottom:12px;">
              Productos solicitados
            </div>
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                   style="border-collapse:collapse;border:1px solid #e6e0d4;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;">
              <thead>
                <tr style="background-color:#eef4e3;">
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:10px 12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">#</th>
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:10px 12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Producto</th>
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:10px 12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Categoría</th>
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:10px 12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Calibre</th>
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:10px 12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Calidad</th>
                  <th align="left"   style="padding:10px 12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Formato</th>
                  <th align="center" style="padding:10px 12px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#3d5a08;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;border-bottom:1px solid #dde8cc;">Cant.</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
              {% for item in items %}
                <tr style="background-color:{{ loop.index is odd ? '#ffffff' : '#faf8f4' }};">
                  <td style="padding:11px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#a09880;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">{{ item.line }}</td>
                  <td style="padding:11px 12px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a2e1c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">{{ item.product }}</td>
                  <td style="padding:11px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#4a5e4c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">{{ item.category != '-' ? item.category : '—' }}</td>
                  <td style="padding:11px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#4a5e4c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">{{ item.caliber != '-' ? item.caliber : '—' }}</td>
                  <td style="padding:11px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#4a5e4c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">{{ item.quality != '-' ? item.quality : '—' }}</td>
                  <td style="padding:11px 12px;font-size:12px;color:#4a5e4c;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">{{ item.format != '-' ? item.format : '—' }}</td>
                  <td align="center" style="padding:11px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #ede8df;">
                    <span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#567f0b;color:#ffffff;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;min-width:26px;text-align:center;">
                      {{ item.quantity }}
                    </span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              {% endfor %}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── CTA button ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="padding:32px 36px 0;">
            <a href="{{ reviewUrl }}"
               style="display:inline-block;background-color:#80ba1b;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 40px;border-radius:8px;letter-spacing:0.3px;">
              Revisar pedido
            </a>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- ── Footer ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px 36px 36px;">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td style="border-top:1px solid #e6e0d4;padding-top:22px;text-align:center;">
                  {% if logoPequenoUrl %}
                    <img src="{{ logoPequenoUrl }}" alt="Citribio"
                         style="display:block;margin:0 auto 12px;height:32px;width:auto;max-width:120px;opacity:0.7;" />
                  {% endif %}
                  <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#567f0b;">Citribio — Gestión de pedidos</p>
                  <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#a09880;line-height:1.6;">
                    Este es un mensaje automático generado por el sistema de pedidos de Citribio.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
      <!-- /email card -->

    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
